{"title":"复燃[恋之埋火]","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":512,"tags":["2020小学期"],"operation":{"submit":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1197#submit_code","submissions":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/submissions?problem_id=1197","statistics":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1197/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1197/testdata","discussion":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/discussion/problem/1197"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"有一个由0/1组成的字符串 $s$ 初始是空，你对它进行了 $n$ 次操作，一共有三种可供选择的操作，分别是：\r\n\r\n1. 在 $s$ 末尾插入一个 $0$.\r\n2. 在 $s$ 末尾插入一个 $1$.\r\n3. 若 $s$ 非空，删除 $s$ 的末尾元素，若 $s$ 为空，那么什么都不会发生（但即使什么都没有发生，仍被视为一次操作）.\r\n\r\n显然，一共有 $3^n$ 种可能的操作序列，恋恋想知道，其中有多少种序列，使得最后得到的字符串 $s$ 为她想要的 $T$ ,答案对 $10^9+7$ 取模输出."},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"第一行一个正整数 $n$.\r\n\r\n第二行一个零一字符串 $T$."},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"一行一个非负整数表示答案取模后的结果."},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"#### 样例输入1\r\n```plain\r\n3\r\n0\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输出1\r\n```plain\r\n5\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输入2\r\n```plain\r\n298\r\n1010101010100\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输出2\r\n```plain\r\n702160232\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输入2\r\n```plain\r\n4000\r\n101010100101010101010101010010000010101011111100101\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输出2\r\n```plain\r\n492748191\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"$1\\leq n\\leq5000$\r\n\r\n$1\\leq |S|\\leq n$"}]}